therian.buildweaver

Annotation Type StandardOperator


  • @Documented
@Target(value={TYPE,FIELD,METHOD})
public @interface StandardOperator
    For use by Therian's build-weaver plugin module. Marks an Operator for inclusion in Operators#standard(). When used on a (non-abstract) class, a default constructor will be used to instantiate the class. When used on a static field, that field's value will be used. When used on a static method, the return value from an invocation of that method will be used.
